Updated 21 August 2002

CORE PACKAGES
microwindows-0.89pre9.tar.gz		base distribution
microwindows-fonts-0.89pre9.tar.gz	free truetype, chinese, japanese, korean fonts
freetype-1.3.1.tar.gz			libttf.so - freetype font engine
jpegsrc.v6b.tar.gz			libjpeg.a - JPEG image library
png-1.0.5.tar.gz			libpng.a - PNG image library
zlib-1.1.3.tar.gz			libz.a - compression lib for loadable pcf.gz fonts/png files
t1lib-1.0.tar.gz			libt1.a - T1 font engine
ime-beta-1.patch			chinese input method editor (untested)
alpha.diff				alpha blending patch (soon to be included core)

DEMONSTRATION SCRIPTS
chess.sh	chess game demo
demo.sh		win32 api (singly linked apps w/server) demos
demo2.sh	simple multiple apps demo
fontdemo.sh	freetype font demo, clipped/rotated ft demo
fontdemo2.sh	logical font descriptors, ft/t1 antialias and rotation demo
fontdemo3.sh	PCF loadable font demo (uses /usr/lib/X11/fonts dir)
grdemo.sh	graphics operations demo
indent.sh	Microwindows coding style indentation reformatter
launcher.sh	sample desktop with great screensavers (wait 10 secs)
mouse.sh	start gpm mouse driver
nxterm.sh	terminal emulator, screen kbd demo
nxview.sh	image viewer demo
vnc.sh		VNC client demo

BINARIES (run in demo scripts above)
bin/mdemo	Microwindows 3d demo (win32 api)
bin/mterm	Microwindows terminal emulator (win32 api)
bin/malpha	Microwindows alpha blending (win32 api)
bin/nano-X	Nano-X server (must be run before Nano-X demos) (see *.sh)
bin/nanowm	Nano-X Window Manager (run after nano-X, see *.sh)

OPTIONAL LIBRARIES
sdl-1.1.3c.tar.gz			NX SDL library
flnx-0.16.tar.gz			NX FLTK library
Nanogtk-1.0.tar.gz			GTK+ port to NX
tinywidgets-0.1.tar.gz			NX C widget library
nxlib-0.4.tar.gz			X11 -> NX conversion library (unreleased)
qt-x11.2.3.1.tar.gz			X11 C++ Qt library w/qtconf.sh, qtfix.sh

APPS
dvdview-1.1.0c.tar.gz			NX mpeg player (single threaded, direct fb map) (16-32bpp)
smpeg-0.4.0c.tar.gz			NX/SDL mpeg player (multi-threaded)
nxdoom-src.tar.gz			NX Doom (8bpp only) (seperate doom1.wad required)
nxfreecell-0.1.tar.gz			NX freecell (desktop and iPAQ versions?)
nxzilla-source-0.9.4.tar.bz2		NX mozilla
mozilla-devel-0.9.5.tar.gz		mozilla development kit
nxrwin-1.5.0a.tar.gz			NX microsoft RDP client
viewml-0.21.tar.gz			NX ViewML web browser

APPS (requires nxlib X11 library)
xsunclock-1.5				X11 sunclock
xscreensaver-3.26			X11 screen saver graphics demos
xfreecell-1.0.5a			X11 freecell
